summary:
PeterMJ shippers: *sees FFH trailer* MJ knows his identity?? Yes! My OTP is finally happening.
Me: pfff, I can’t wait for a...
body:
PeterMJ shippers: *sees FFH trailer* MJ knows his identity?? Yes! My OTP is finally happening.

Me: pfff, I can’t wait for a future film where Black Cat appears and steals Peter from Mary Jane. Who says you gotta follow through completely with the comics route when it comes to couples?? But seeing as how the MCU has kinda of failed to get the essential Spider-Man characterization right, I’m gonna happily not see it.
